. UK companies can apply, with solutions assessed by jHub — for potential UK defence use.</p>\n</div>","title":"UK and US seek solutions to counter underwater drone threat"},{"document_type":"Case Study","href":"/government/case-studies/filtronic-pioneering-smarter-semiconductor-packaging-for-uk-defence","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69b3d7c5b84f01b2be53a1c4/s712_Filtronic_Case_Study.png","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69b3d7c5e2719934bb53a1c8/s465_Filtronic_Case_Study.png","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69b3d7c5e2719934bb53a1c7/Filtronic_Case_Study.png"},"public_updated_at":"2026-03-12T16:57:21.000+00:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>With DTEP funding, Filtronic has developed cutting-edge plastic packaging technology for high-power semiconductors, strengthening the UK’s independence in critical defence technology.</p>\n</div>","title":"Filtronic: Pioneering Smarter Semiconductor Packaging for UK Defence"},{"document_type":"News story","href":"/government/news/blood-on-demand-ukdi-seeks-innovations-for-blood-testing-in-the-field","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69b29b2597f6fef21f687abe/s712_Blood_on_tap_themed_comp_gov.uk_image.png","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69b29b2559f6a126771258cd/s465_Blood_on_tap_themed_comp_gov.uk_image.png","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69b29b2559f6a126771258ce/Blood_on_tap_themed_comp_gov.uk_image.png"},"public_updated_at":"2026-03-10T12:03:00.000+00:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>This competition requires ideas for optimising the safety of blood used in deployed settings</p>\n</div>","title":"Blood on demand: UKDI seeks innovations for blood testing in the field"}],"ordered_featured_links":[{"href":"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/log-in-or-register-for-a-ukd